      <br />
       Currently, working at <a class="underline" href="https://chordio.com">
        Chordio</a>, developing an AI platform that enables product managers to iterate and prototype rapidly and effectively.
    </p>
  </section>
  <section title='skills'>
    <h2 class='text-xl font-bold'>Skills</h2>
    <p>
