        <h4>Israel Defense Forces (Intelligence Corps/Home Front Command)</h4>
        <h5 class='text-slate-500'>December 2022 - December 2023</h5>
        <p>
          <ul class='marker:text-slate-700 list-disc pl-4 py-4 flex flex-col gap-2'>
            <li>
              Directly and simultaneously led both full stack and data
              engineering teams, totaling 20 professionals.
            </li>
            <li>
              Designed and developed emergency and humanitarian web-based
              systems for national and international crises.
            </li>
          </ul>


        </p>
      </li>
      <li class='exprience'>
        <h3 class='text-xl'>Web Developer</h3>
        <h4>Israel Defense Forces (Intelligence Corps/Home Front Command)</h4>
        <h5 class='text-slate-500'>April 2021 - December 2022</h5>
        <p>
          <ul class='marker:text-slate-700 list-disc pl-4 py-4 flex flex-col gap-2'>
            <li>
              Developed vital systems and national crisis solutions using data
              & web technologies like Node.js, React, MongoDB, and Azure Cloud.
            </li>
            <li>
              Worked in a high-speed, changing environment utilizing public
